::Starlight/Fenox::

Starlight smiles triumphantly as Teltoli falls to the ground. She 
puts away her tranquilizer gun and dives after the Maximal.

Starlight lands near Teltoli, taking Teltoli's rapier by the handle. 
She slices it down at Teltoli's back.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Fenox looks for a new target and spots one. She opens fire on Angel 
Prime.



--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, steph_teltoli@m... wrote:
> Teltoli winces as the two darts hit her, and she puts a hand to 
her, 
> her vision swimming. She groaned quietly, and her wings failed her, 
> sending her in a direct plummet for the ground.
> 
> 'I'm sorry Windlord and Aerotaur..' 
> 
> The hit would have knocked the air out of her lungs, except she was 
> already out cold by the time she landed on her back, eyes closed. 
The 
> shot from Fenox whizzed by her, missed because of her falling.
